{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"PASS 1 (T8 LLM/prompt structural-completeness overlay): No findings. The metrics schema (det_ms / llm_ms / total_ms / llm_calls / claim_path) is fully specified — value vocabulary defined in AC and grounded in gate_dispatch._attach_plan_review_metrics. No undefined-but-referenced enum/protocol, no ambiguous counter placement (llm_calls proxy = finder criteria_count + agent calls is explicit), and the partial/untimed-record fallback (missing duration_ms → 0, never raises) is specified. This is a telemetry-reinstatement plan, not an LLM-agent design, so the overlay applies thinly and passes."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782545855984419001,"uuid":"14fd2383-1fcb-4efb-bf7a-033bb1a2dd0f"}